WEBVTT

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:30.576
To spread hatred or love?

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.200
I leave that decision to you.

00:05:32.258 --> 00:05:36.118
(Applause)

00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:47.456
